{"tid":534514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[美劇] 星空奇遇記：發現號 | Star Trek : Discovery","createTime":"2018-01-20T01:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T14:30:46.000Z","uid":72730,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f78390b5ae94724ae1f717bf33fa4dfdf117ffac","tid":534514,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/084930_718f4919d7387f089d7ddc57eb547999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F084930_718f4919d7387f089d7ddc57eb547999.jpg&h=025fa36a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事設定於原創影集的大約十年前，《星空奇遇記：發現號》將會呈現一個全新的紀元，回到最初追溯聯盟的過去。戰爭的威脅逐漸迫近, 第一少校Michael Burnham (Sonequa Martin-Green) 還要同時面對新船艦、新世界和新反派的沖擊。 《星空奇遇記：發現號》將於今個秋季於 Netflix 初次登場。<br />\n<br />\n星際聯邦太空邊緣發現了潛伏物之後，星際艦隊就再也不一樣。 探索星艦迷航記的全新紀元，由9月25日起，於 Netflix每週上線。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">- Netflix正式預告 -</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yj2mmeCh20s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYj2mmeCh20s&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0cbc844a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yj2mmeCh20s</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TTVQWS9Y3f4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTTVQWS9Y3f4&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e9976fc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TTVQWS9Y3f4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>- Opening Titles -</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wX1byq2C9ng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwX1byq2C9ng&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6f14f45b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wX1byq2C9ng</a>"},{"pid":"9523d2e0b8be7a6d494a46ea1690f1502eb05cad","tid":534514,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_f1c9273ad8cf1639cf1a3050d1a9942c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_f1c9273ad8cf1639cf1a3050d1a9942c.jpg&h=53e0acfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_38a4dbe8740544532a34951da67b5272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_38a4dbe8740544532a34951da67b5272.jpg&h=8a40a4af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_dd8b48ed7b3493bb06fdfd8a9622631b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_dd8b48ed7b3493bb06fdfd8a9622631b.jpg&h=61ca30d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_e5572b001fed3665985c66fa4ec0bd7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_e5572b001fed3665985c66fa4ec0bd7c.jpg&h=b4df4323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091158_363ff2672460f17d8d3d5c1ee0850223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091158_363ff2672460f17d8d3d5c1ee0850223.jpg&h=5b18ff15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_c5fa8c870062833f763f05b8383bf43b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_c5fa8c870062833f763f05b8383bf43b.jpg&h=4c0b68f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091156_fe68a27b7563434b3bc831c4e69a9a4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091156_fe68a27b7563434b3bc831c4e69a9a4e.jpg&h=0299ac66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091157_661f7b750d54e336242f8298ac0559a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091157_661f7b750d54e336242f8298ac0559a8.jpg&h=806e7bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091157_9c78017458d67e819b948e912a25c319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091157_9c78017458d67e819b948e912a25c319.jpg&h=7570ffa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091157_f89bee98eff27f59e70f153cb96cd44f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091157_f89bee98eff27f59e70f153cb96cd44f.jpg&h=7942e67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/091157_0b033a30f27cd3c0072298f576d6f8f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F091157_0b033a30f27cd3c0072298f576d6f8f7.jpg&h=4a4b8b25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53c76d3b84d2ad0e00dd4ecb065b6626346ec44e","tid":534514,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Michael Burnham</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/092415_51c4201bcc27eba33cb5e4df4bc67490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F092415_51c4201bcc27eba33cb5e4df4bc67490.jpg&h=34c2a595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯邦星艦神舟號大副，被瓦肯人收養的人類，言行充滿瓦肯人極度理性的作風。戰爭爆發前，襲擊自己的艦長以試圖阻止戰爭，但未成功；戰爭爆發後被軍事法庭判定抗命，逐出艦隊入監服刑。後接受發現號艦長洛卡招募，藉由發現號監管的方式加入發現號科學部，經過多次任務考驗後，洛卡艦長授予科學官職務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Gabriel Lorca</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/092816_d5383011ada5be00cfe3bb2190eb4735.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F092816_d5383011ada5be00cfe3bb2190eb4735.JPG&h=96fe72d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現號艦長。擁有著輝煌紀錄的軍事戰術家。雙眼因為舊傷，無法承受突然的光線變化。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Saru</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/092519_5e3dec669ef773127592147ffe6e2d33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F092519_5e3dec669ef773127592147ffe6e2d33.jpg&h=0e1d0d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現號的大副。水魔族，天性敏感，能感應到危險的接近。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Paul Stamets</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/092601_9c57190450666744d2374adef87f3c6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F092601_9c57190450666744d2374adef87f3c6c.jpg&h=b521f4b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現號首席科學官。專長是研究太空菌種，孢子驅動系統設計者。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sylvia Tilly</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/20/092728_eeb81c5b7d7a7815954b209aa3ef7d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F092728_eeb81c5b7d7a7815954b209aa3ef7d46.jpg&h=a2cd5979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星際艦隊學院學員，麥珂的室友。在學最後一年的實習被分配到發現號，隸屬科學部。生性極度樂觀，訓練有素但缺乏實戰經驗。對聚酯與聚氨酯纖維（物質合成機的主要原料）過敏，因此她的制服與寢具需要特別配置。以當上艦長為目標，接受麥珂的訓練與指導。"},{"pid":"1bf18a9fd94413073e14856bfa5112c2fa476cf1","tid":534514,"uid":42626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T17:43:51.000Z","msg":"播返無人睇？平行宇宙開始勁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb6c54c9f3996d83ccec6efb0a762a66f5719aa","tid":534514,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf18a9fd944